name: Felicia (Darkstalkers/Vampire)
description:
I was surprised such a popular character didn't have a LoRA, so I made one. It might need a second epoch as her hands are a bit messed up, but that's normal with diffused images anyway so who knows.

Quirks:
If you don't prompt for blue hair then her hair will be purple occasionally.
Prompting the tail in improves the overall result

As Usual:
Trained on Anything v3
Demos are Anything v4.5 with LoRA weight 0.9 this time
Lowered the EasyNegative to 0.8 as well figuring it might mess with her unusual hands/feet
